10: Hold still and lemme beat your ass!
17:
Form into a power that will pierce
my foe! Gladius!
22: Phew... That should be all of them.
26:
No one seems hurt either, luckily.
Let's get these golems cleared out
of the way so no one trips on them.
47:
Thank you for the save back there!
What's your name?
55:
Nice to meet you, Hibiki. I'm Luciada.
If you ever need anything at all, I'd
be happy to help. It's the least I can
do.
59:
That's... okay. I just did what anyone
else would do.
64:
Hold on, I knew I recognized that
face!
68:
You're one of the people we found in
the Kaleidoscope not too long ago!
73:
Ah. One of the people who returned
from the Abyss.
77:
Yeah... That's what they tell me. I
don't really know all the details.
85:
No thanks needed! I'm just glad to
see you're doing better!
88:
So you're a teleporter, huh? That's a
sick power! You can sleep in all you
want and still make it on time for
stuff!
92:
...It's not that amazing. I can't use it
much since it tires me out right
away... And...
95:
It's not like I can use it to go back to
Japan...
103:
But I wouldn't worry about it. Life's
just as good here once you get used to
it.
116:
Suminami, you can come to us if
you ever need anything. We're here
for you.
131:
Hibiki, as your new neighbor, I hope
we can be friends. Maybe even work
together in the future, if you're willing.
135:
"We'll make our dreams come true
together, one step at a time..." That's
what you wrote on your flyers, right?
144:
Do you really think it'd be that easy
to make it happen?
151:
And who invited those Shibuya
weirdos? They—
154:
I don't know about easy, but I
believe it can happen.
166:
Ah... Ahaha! I suppose it's only
natural to criticize your leaders.
177:
I suppose it's what I have to believe
in, no matter what.
180:
As a member of House Sextan, I
have a vested interest in making
sure that Palpebra and Shibuya
remain on good terms.
183:
And maybe if this festival is a
success...
186:
I'll have earned my place as student
council president.
189: But that's easier said than done.
197:
Luciada, what would you like to
come from this Magia Fest?
201: What... do you mean by that?
204:
I mean, I want relations to improve
between us and Shibuya—
208:
No, none of that. I don't want to hear
the reasons you tell yourself. I want
to know how you truly feel.
211: Tell me: what do you truly wish to do?
221:
Sorry to bother you, but I found this
back where you fought the golems. I
think someone dropped it.
224:
O-oh, thank you. I'll see if I can't
locate its owner.
235:
I just took out all my anger on some
stranger...
238:
Is this really the kind of person I want
to be...
246:
I expect nothing less of my
Palpebran rivals! Even their students
are capable of masterful cooking!
249: You there! You must try a bite of this!
258:
No need to be polite! Try it! Your
taste buds will thank you!
